      "blocks": {
        "text_3Pc6HP": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "The Gntl Standard",
            "title_size": 3,
            "text": "<p>At Gntl, we believe in minimalist skincare that works effortlessly for both face and body. Our high-performance formulations are crafted with purpose, delivering exceptional results through simplified routines while maintaining our commitment to conscious ingredient selection.</p>",
            "body_size": 5,
            "text_align": "text-left"
          }
        },
        "text_hk7PBN": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Our Clean Commitment ",
            "title_size": 3,
            "text": "<p>We believe in minimalist, multifunctional skincare that's genuinely clean. Our products are formulated without over 2,700 ingredients that are restricted or prohibited by the EU and major clean beauty retailers.</p><p>We thoughtfully exclude: </p><p>Parabens, Phthalates, Mineral oil + petroleum derivatives, Formaldehyde & formaldehyde-releasing agents, Oxybenzone + octinoxate, Coal tar, Hydroquinone, Triclosan + triclocarban, BHA + BHT, Aluminum salts, Lead & mercury, PEGs + ethoxylated ingredients, Nanoparticles, Silicones, Synthetic dyes, Talc, Ethanolamines (like DEA, TEA, MEA), Sodium Lauryl Sulfate (SLS), Propylene Glycol, and many others...</p><p>Our clean philosophy promise means <strong>everything you want, and nothing you don’t</strong>: effective, luxurious skincare that puts your well-being and the planet first. Gntl’s alignment with the Credo Clean Standard is our commitment to you – delivering results you can feel good about, with safety and sustainability at the forefront.</p>",
            "body_size": 5,
            "text_align": "text-left"
          }
        },
        "text_az3RQk": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Contact us",
            "title_size": 3,
            "text": "<p>If you have any suggestions on how Gntl can improve our impact, please drop us a line at <a href=\"mailto:hello@gntlskin.com\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">hello@gntlskin.com</span></a>.</p>",
            "body_size": 5,
            "text_align": "text-left"
          }
        }
